data.description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED FOR 28th! SELLER IS OFFERING 10K IN SELLER CONCESSIONS OR RATE BUY DOWN!!!!! BACK ON MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF HOME OR SELLER, BUYER COULD NOT OBTAIN FINANCING!!! This stunning custom-built home sits atop a hill and boasts panoramic views that will take your breath away. Imagine waking up each morning to the sun rising over the horizon and enjoying your morning coffee while taking in the picturesque landscape. This is the perfect place to unwind and escape from the hustle and bustle of city life. With 8 acres of land, this property offers plenty of room for outdoor activities, entertaining, and exploration. This two-story home features 5 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The Owner's suite has been remodeled and is nicely done. The second full bathroom is also remodeled, as well as the kitchen. The property also includes a spacious deck off the second floor, a covered back patio with a wet bar in the back on patio. Bring your horses, chickens and goats!!
